Here&#39;s one way to crawl seeds only, and not even embedded images or anything, which seems to be what you want. Starting with the default order.xml...

1. remove the scope rule acceptIfSurtPrefixed
2. remove the scope rule acceptIfTranscluded
3. add this scope rule right after rejectByDefault
    &lt;newObject name=&quot;acceptIfSeed&quot; class=&quot;org.archive.crawler.deciderules.SeedAcceptDecideRule&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/newObject&gt;

Hope this works for you.

Noah


